' PHASE 10 — DEVOPS
' ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

|**PHASE 10**\nDevOps|

:🚀 **PHASE 10 — DevOps & déploiement**
~~1 semaine~~;

fork
  :Dockerfile Spring Boot
  multi-stage
  FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jdk;
fork again
  :Dockerfile Next.js
  multi-stage
  FROM node:20-alpine;
end fork

:docker-compose.prod.yml
app + gateway + postgres
+ redis + n8n;

:Variables d'environnement
Secrets GitHub Actions
(API keys, DB, JWT secret);

fork
  :Pipeline CI — Tests
  push → mvn test + pnpm test;
fork again
  :Pipeline CD — Build
  build image → push
  GitHub Container Registry;
fork again
  :Pipeline CD — Deploy
  SSH → docker compose
  pull + up (staging);
end fork

fork
  :Spring Actuator + Prometheus
  /health + /metrics exposés;
fork again
  :Dashboard Grafana
  CPU / latence / erreurs;
end fork

:Domaine + SSL HTTPS
nginx reverse proxy
+ Let's Encrypt;

:🟢 **PRODUCTION**
Application live et opérationnelle;

note right
  Livrables :
  - Images Docker buildées
  - CI/CD GitHub Actions actif
  - Staging déployé et testé
  - Monitoring Grafana actif
  - HTTPS configuré
end note

stop

@enduml
